    "text": [
        "Hello Sir,",
        "Hope you are doing good!",
        "I am writing this letter to you in regards to my six months transition period in the head office of Sydney, which I was looking for a move to acquire some work experience with hands-on testing. As I have been offered the opportunity from the main head office and hope you must be aware of this.",
        "I will need your support to manage my work here in the current office location. I will be required a few subordinates can lead my work to deliver on time to the business, as I would away from work.",
